title: Tiny Desk Contest Top Shelf: Episode 2 With Phoebe Bridgers
description: Before we announce this year's Tiny Desk Contest winner, we're asking our judges to share their favorite entries in a weekly livestreamed series. In this episode, Phoebe Bridgers shares her picks.
